    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Oddly enough, it now sounds even smoother! The III7 trick is so common in J-pop that our ears have fully accepted it. ‚ÄúBitter‚Äù and ‚Äúsweet‚Äù are relative; habits change."
        }
      ]
    },
    { "type": "paragraph", "children": [{ "text": "" }] },
    { "type": "heading-one", "children": [{ "text": "Modal Interchange in Daily Life" }] },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [{ "text": "The same tension-release recipe is everywhere:" }]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "‚Ä¢ Movie plot twists‚Äîfirst the uncomfortable suspense, then the happy ending."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        { "text": "‚Ä¢ Food pairings‚Äîsweet cake with a swipe of bitter matcha." }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "‚Ä¢ Friday euphoria‚Äîmid-summer vacation may feel dull, but the last class on Friday always thrills."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        { "text": "Composers simply translate this psychology into sound." }
      ]
    },
    { "type": "paragraph", "children": [{ "text": "" }] },
    {
      "type": "heading-one",
      "children": [{ "text": "From Feelings to Formulas ‚Äì The Pro‚Äôs ‚ÄúSecret Spice Rack‚Äù" }]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "That ‚Äútension first, comfort after‚Äù rule is a golden law. For centuries musicians have distilled it into ready-to-use formulas."
        }
      ]
    },
    { "type": "paragraph", "children": [{ "text": "" }] },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "We mentioned the 5-1 cadence last time: V is unstable, I is stable, 5-1 is the clearest ‚Äúuncomfortable‚Üícomfortable‚Äù move‚Ä¶"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "So why not hijack that 5-1 energy and manufacture extra tension-release pockets wherever we want?"
        }
      ]
    },
    { "type": "paragraph", "children": [{ "text": "" }] },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Here‚Äôs a plain C-major I (Cmaj) ‚Üí IV (Fmaj) progression:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "roll",
      "id": "modulation-4",
      "data": {
        "tracks": [
          {
            "range": ["C4", "C6"],
            "instrument": "piano",
